    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think it's good to have a widget for errors. However I would (as a developper) like to have a way to integrate such error feedback in my programmatic js (to implement popups logic or conditionnally display part of an instantsearch UI), which seems awkward with a widget. How do you think it could work @olance ?",
