    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think @vvo sees #1585 as a quick fix for the fact that we currently have no easy error handling in instantsearch.js... and the widget as a nice/convenient way to display an error when you're not doing too low-level things.\r\n\r\nAt least that's how I see it...\r\nTo me it's kind of the same as having a `render` event and a `hits` widget :)",
